<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pardon-vt">pardon <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɑːdn/    美 /'pɑːrdn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-forgive">1.★ <strong>[正式用语] [不用于进行时] 原谅；宽恕 (forgive)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Pardon</strong> me <strong>for</strong> interrupting you.
对不起，打扰你了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can you read the sign, sir? No smoking allowed in the lift!
先生，请看一下告示牌好吗？电梯里禁止吸烟！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— <strong>Pardon me</strong>.
对不起。</p></div></div>